&lt;li&gt;Experience writing detailed functional specifications for transactional systems (orders, inventory, fulfillment, manufacturing) where the domain model directly determines product capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Domain expertise in manufacturing, fulfillment, ERP systems

